               <p>DENNIS JOHNSON. I am in partnership with John Allen - we are <rs id="t18260406-102-viclabel530" type="occupation">coach-makers</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-102-victim622 t18260406-102-viclabel530"></join>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-102-victim623 t18260406-102-viclabel530"></join>. This apron has been cut off our pheaton; this small strap which I have in my hand was left nailed on the pheaton. I know nothing of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260406-102-person624">
                  THOMAS 
                  CARY
